{
  "category": "Uncategorized",
  "description": "Remove Rounded Corners from Full-Width Sections\n\nUpdate the styling for all full-width sections to have square corners instead of rounded corners, starting with the counter-section.\n\nRequirements:\n- Remove border-radius styling from the counter-section component\n- Audit all other full-width sections in the application for rounded corners\n- Apply consistent square corner styling across all full-width sections\n- Ensure container or wrapper sections that span the full viewport width have border-radius: 0\n- Verify that sections with constrained widths retain their existing corner styling\n- Test responsive behavior to confirm styling applies correctly at all breakpoints",
